HEADWORD: Kinkhaust
<hw>Kink"haust`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prov. E.
<ets>kink</ets> to gasp (cf. <er>Chin cough</er>) + <ets>haust</ets> a
cough (akin to E. <ets>wheeze</ets>).]</ety> <def>Whooping cough.</def>
